publishingInformation.testingInstructions:
alexa jensenstyle minecraft
alexa start
the answer to the startup question is how do you drive this thing

This starts our private on-demand minecraft server that our kids and their friends use to play minecraft together. The start intent is configured to ask for a password and validate it before the intent is allowed (simple way of securing the access without need for oauth).
